    public class ComponentCalcul
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
implements SendTupleImplementationI, CreateCalculServiceI
    The class ComponentCalcul implements a component that can perform some computational tasks

    The component implements the SendTupleImplementationI interface to send tuple to other component and it implements also l'interface CreateCalculServiceI to execute calculate tasks

    作者:
    Yajie LIU, Zimeng ZHANG
